Recommends: podman, docker.io
Description: Manage Podman and other container engines from a single UI
 Podman Desktop provides a graphical interface for managing Podman and
 other container engines like Docker. It includes a system tray icon
 for quick access to container management functions.
 .
 Features include:
  - Container and image management
  - Multi-engine support (Podman, Docker)
  - System tray integration
  - Comprehensive UI for container operations